I CAN ASSURE YOU,

28:14.580 --> 28:15.512
WE ARE UTILIZING
ALL OF OUR RESOURCES

28:15.550 --> 28:17.370
TO SERVE MAX.

28:17.410 --> 28:19.105
- SO WHAT, THAT'S IT?

28:19.140 --> 28:19.993
THAT'S WHAT YOU'RE GONNA DO?
THAT'S IT?

28:20.040 --> 28:21.246
- THAT'S NOT WHAT I'M SAYING
AT ALL.

28:21.280 --> 28:23.862
I'M SAYING
IT'S A TOUGH SITUATION,

28:23.900 --> 28:25.310
AND WE ARE DOING
OUR BEST.

28:25.350 --> 28:28.387
- WELL, I THINK THAT YOUR BEST
IS UNACCEPTABLE.

28:28.430 --> 28:31.046
I REALLY DO.

