- YOU KNOW, THIS, UM,

28:42.340 --> 28:44.888
ITALIAN ROAST STUFF
IS PRETTY GOOD, YOU KNOW?

28:44.930 --> 28:46.716
- RIGHT, ISN'T IT?

28:46.750 --> 28:48.718
ISN'T IT WONDERFUL?
- YEAH.

28:50.760 --> 28:52.580
PRETTY STRANGE BEING HERE
WITHOUT YOU, MILLIE.

28:52.620 --> 28:55.726
- [laughs]
YEAH, I'LL BET.

28:55.760 --> 28:58.274
- I MEAN, A BIG HOUSE,
JUST ME.

28:58.320 --> 28:59.218
- WELL, THE KIDS CAME BY,
DIDN'T THEY?

28:59.250 --> 29:02.219
- YEAH, KIDS CAME BY.
THAT WAS GREAT.

29:02.250 --> 29:03.899
THAT WAS NICE.

29:06.260 --> 29:10.356
YOU KNOW, I DIDN'T LIKE
BEING HERE WITHOUT YOU.

29:10.400 --> 29:13.437
AND NOW, UM,

29:13.470 --> 29:14.949
NOW THAT YOU'RE BACK,

29:14.990 --> 29:18.983
YOU'RE NOT ALL THE WAY BACK,
YOU KNOW?

29:19.030 --> 29:22.648
NOT ALL OF YOU IS HERE.

29:22.690 --> 29:23.714
[snickers]

29:23.760 --> 29:25.273
- [laughs]
I'M ALL HERE.

29:25.310 --> 29:27.278
- NO, I DON'T--I DON'T MEAN IT
IN A BAD WAY.

29:27.310 --> 29:29.756
YOU WENT OUT THERE,
AND YOU HAD

29:29.800 --> 29:33.270
THIS WONDERFUL ADVENTURE,
THIS--

29:33.320 --> 29:35.242
GOT A TASTE FOR LIFE.

29:35.290 --> 29:37.929
AND YOU'RE HAPPY.

29:37.980 --> 29:41.188
YOU'RE THE HAPPIEST
I'VE EVER SEEN YOU.

29:41.220 --> 29:42.801
- WELL, THAT'S A GOOD THING,
RIGHT?

29:42.850 --> 29:44.499
- YEAH.
YEAH, IT'S A GOOD THING.

29:47.880 --> 29:50.462
THE BAD THING, SWEETHEART,
IS THAT, UH,

29:50.510 --> 29:53.673
I CAN'T HELP BUT...

29:53.720 --> 29:56.780
FEEL THAT...

29:56.820 --> 29:58.856
I WAS THE ONE
THAT WAS HOLDING YOU BACK

29:58.900 --> 30:03.132
FROM BEING HAPPY.

30:03.180 --> 30:05.580
- I JUST NEEDED
A LITTLE ADVENTURE.

30:05.630 --> 30:07.109
THAT'S ALL.

30:09.320 --> 30:11.356
- I DON'T WANT
TO LOSE YOU, MILLIE.

30:11.390 --> 30:13.210
- YOU'RE NOT LOSING ME.

30:13.250 --> 30:17.664
- SEE, WHILE YOU WERE GONE,
I REALIZED THAT, UH...

30:17.710 --> 30:20.326
OH, GOD.

30:20.370 --> 30:22.531
IT'S HARD.

30:22.570 --> 30:23.537
[exhales]

30:23.580 --> 30:26.743
WELL, I--

30:26.790 --> 30:29.998
IN OUR MARRIAGE, THAT...

30:30.030 --> 30:31.406
YOU'RE THE ONE THAT'S MADE
MOST OF THE COMPROMISES.

30:31.450 --> 30:35.090
YOU'RE THE ONE THAT'S DONE
MOST OF THE SACRIFICING.

30:35.140 --> 30:36.471
YOU'VE BEEN HERE
FOR THE FAMILY.

30:36.520 --> 30:39.068
ALL THE TIME.

30:39.110 --> 30:42.694
AND IF SELLING THIS HOUSE
IS IMPORTANT TO YOU,

30:42.730 --> 30:44.903
AND I KNOW IT IS,

30:44.940 --> 30:46.350
THEN I'M WILLING
TO DO THAT.

30:46.390 --> 30:49.632
FOR YOU.

30:49.670 --> 30:51.217
FOR US.

30:51.260 --> 30:54.809
BECAUSE BEING IN THIS HOUSE
WITHOUT YOU

30:54.850 --> 30:57.887
IS JUST NOT GONNA WORK.

31:07.450 --> 31:12.274
- OKAY. OKAY, JABBAR'S
IN THE SHOWER.

31:12.310 --> 31:13.379
I FOUND A CLEAN PAIR OF PANTS
IN A BAG

31:13.420 --> 31:15.797
THAT DIDN'T EVEN HAVE
CLOTHES IN IT.

31:15.830 --> 31:16.489
BUT, I MEAN,
HE'S NOT GONNA MATCH,

31:16.520 --> 31:17.908
BUT THEY'RE AT LEAST CLEAN.

31:17.940 --> 31:19.521
